msgid "set_linear_damp(value)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody.rst:414
msgid "get_linear_damp()"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody.rst:417
msgid ""
"The body's linear damp. Cannot be less than -1.0. If this value is "
"different from -1.0, any linear damp derived from the world or areas will"
" be overridden."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody.rst:423
msgid ":ref:`Vector3 <class_Vector3>` **linear_velocity**"
msgstr ""

