msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody.rst:430
msgid "get_linear_velocity()"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_rigidbody.rst:433
msgid ""
"The body's linear velocity. Can be used sporadically, but **don't set "
"this every frame**, because physics may run in another thread and runs at"
" a different granularity. Use :ref:`_integrate_forces "
"<class_RigidBody_method__integrate_forces>` as your process loop for "
"precise control of the body state."
msgstr ""

